---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact | Cutler Capital Management">
  <main id="main">
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
        <h1>A calm, low-pressure conversation.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Most relationships begin by comparing how we think. If our philosophy resonates, we’d welcome a discussion.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container two-col">
        <div>
          <h2>How to reach us</h2>
          <p>
            Please send a brief note and we will respond promptly. If helpful, include what you’re looking for (strategy materials, planning discussion, institutional due diligence, etc.).
          </p>

          <div class="callout">
            <div class="callout-inner">
              <div>
                <h3 class="callout-title">Office</h3>
                <p class="muted">The Day Building, 306 Main Street, Worcester, MA 01608-1518</p>
              </div>
              <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/firm/">Firm details</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="callout">
            <div class="callout-inner">
              <div>
                <h3 class="callout-title">Phone</h3>
                <p class="muted">For scheduled conversations.</p>
              </div>
              <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:+15087574455">508-757-4455</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="small muted">
            Note: This site provides general information only. Any strategy discussion will be shared in a context appropriate for the recipient.
          </p>
        </div>

        <aside class="side-card">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>What we’ll typically ask</h3>
            <ul class="checklist">
              <li>Time horizon and objectives</li>
              <li>Liquidity needs and constraints</li>
              <li>Risk tolerance framed as permanent loss</li>
              <li>Governance and decision process</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="card-note">
              <p class="small muted">We aim to be explicit about fit and tradeoffs, including periods when we may underperform.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
